Starting school early is very important and help students organizing their time in a useful way. If student start their day lately, their daily life will change in random ways. As a result the sleeping time will change and that effects their bodies and their minds. The body needs more sleeping hours night and not sleeping hour at the day. Unfortunately, teenagers don't know the importance of time, if they start at 10:00 in the morning, they will be late and come sleepy to schools and they will be less focused.